                "key": "Whitemoon Bristle",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>CRIT Rate is increased by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">4%/5%/6%/7%/8%</span>. When Normal Attacks deal Elemental DMG, the Foliar Incision effect will be obtained, increasing DMG dealt by Normal Attacks and Elemental Skills by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">120%/150%/180%/210%/240%</span> of Elemental Mastery. This effect will disappear after 28 DMG instances or 12s. You can obtain Foliar Incision once every 12s.</p>"
                ]
